profile:
Stop wasting your time cleaning. VIP Cleaning Services offers house cleaning services, maid service, commercial and residential maid services that get your house looking its best without you having to lift a finger. Serves Toronto, Scarborough and Etobicoke. You will love having more time to do the things you need to do without having to worry about cleaning house.

Our Expert Cleaning Services Include:
• House Cleaning/Condo Cleaning
• Renovation Cleaning
• Move-In/Move-Out
• Office Cleaning
• Open House Cleaning

We Always Give You VIP Treatment
When you need cleaning services, turn to the professionals with more than a decade of experience. It doesn't take a lot to learn how to clean, but in our decade, we've perfected customer service. No job is too big or small.

profile:
Welcome to V Cleaning Inc.

We are a well-established commercial janitorial and office cleaning service,  providing services in the GTA/GTHA and surrounding area. 

Offering 24/7, eco-friendly services with over 20 years of experience in the cleaning industry, we are able to provide high-quality services at affordable prices. We recognize the value of cleanliness standards on each property.  We provide a service that matches your needs and are bonded and fully insured.

We would appreciate the opportunity to discuss how we can provide a competitive quote.

Covid protocols are strictly adhered to and we offer numerous cleaning services to ensure safety of your Staff and Customers. In these unprecedented times and as a effort to help business impacted by Covid-19, we are responding by offering superior cleaning and sanitization solutions for businesses and facilities.

We got you covered.

We look forward to serving you.

Stay healthy and safe.

Eric Karas
Founder, CEO
